title: Fredericks & Mae Star Domino Set
description:
The Star Domino set replaces typical dots with silkscreened stars used to communicate numbers 0-6. The game's inspiration comes from the pattern's resemblance to Venetian Carnival masks known as Domino, which were white with black spots. A modern visual take on the classic game. Constructed of Baltic Birch, ink, and paper.

Wooden case is 3 in. W x 9 in. L x 2 in. H
